<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="on-top-of">on top of</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>在…之上；加之：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>That high mountain has a tower on top of it. 
那座高山顶上有一座塔。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He gave me a meal and, on top of that, money for my journey. 
他管了我一顿饭，除此之外，还给了我路费。</p></div></div>